{"tid":2150063,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（拋磚引玉）呢張關係圖只係冰山一角，有冇大佬解救！","createTime":"2020-08-10T18:38:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T12:38:17.000Z","uid":348168,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c6c37eb299c584112057f55094c5e05192d121e1","tid":2150063,"uid":348168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T18:38:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dQqQXOE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdQqQXOE.png&h=a5045b9c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n背景故事：<br />\n我和一個寡婦結了婚，她已經有個成年的女兒，我叫她繼女。<br />\n我繼女和我父親結了婚，所以我叫我的繼女做後媽，而我的父親成了我女婿。<br />\n一年後，我和老婆生了個男孩，他是我後媽同母異父的弟弟。<br />\n我兒子叫我爸爸，而我就叫他舅父。<br />\n我繼女和我父親又生了一個男孩，他是我弟弟，而他卻叫我做外公。<br />\n我是我老婆的丈夫，而我老婆卻是我後媽的母親。<br />\n而我則成為了自己的外公？"},{"pid":"e5cde583cde745e456e88d3c14819de405db93e2","tid":2150063,"uid":43556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T19:01:55.000Z","msg":"so?"},{"pid":"791f379f4aabcbc9a917f136afde3e06cf93ac43","tid":2150063,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:14:46.000Z","msg":"多謝呀公！"},{"pid":"090dd4a71a2b39f71472bac236f68c42683e96a6","tid":2150063,"uid":346602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T12:38:17.000Z","msg":"已like"}]}